Â°Â°Â° Navigation Â°Â°Â°
~~~~           ~~~~
Â°Â°Â° Global Navigation: The navigation leading to Top-Level of a Page. Can be included in "navigation bars, drop-down menus, and flyout menus." Â°Â°Â°
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Â°Â°Â° Skip To LinkÂ°Â°Â°
<a href="#main" class="skip-link button">Skip to Main</a>

Â°Â°Â° When clicked this output goes to this main:
<main id="main">
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Â°Â°Â° Hide Content Â°Â°Â°
visually-hidden:not(:focus):not(:active)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Â°Â°Â° Creating Navigation Â°Â°Â°
<nav aria-labelledby="tocTitle">
  <p id="tocTitle">Only on GitHub</p>
...
</nav>
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Â°Â°Â° On This Page Navigation Â°Â°Â°
<nav aria-label="Table of Contents">
  <p>On this page</p>
...
</nav>
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Â°Â°Â° Nav for Screen Readers Â°Â°Â°
<nav aria-labelledby="tocTitle">
  <p id="tocTitle">On this page</p>
  <ul role="list">
    <li>
      <a href="#skip">Skip to content link</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#toc">Table of contents</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#bc">Page Fragments</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#ln">Local navigation</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#global">Global navigation</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</nav>

Â°Â°Â°Note: Remember never change the "tab" order! Â°Â°Â°
