Â°Â°Â° The "<nav>" element,tells assistive technologies to present the breadcrumbs as a navigational element on the current page. Â°Â°Â°
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Â°Â°Â° Separators && Breadcrumb ğŸ¥ªÂ°Â°Â°
[aria-label^="breadcrumbs" i] li + li::before {
  content: "";
  display: block;
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-top: 2px solid currentColor;
  border-right: 2px solid currentColor;
  rotate: 45deg;
  opacity: .8
}
